# Trivy Ignore File
# ------------------
# This file contains CVEs that Trivy flags but cannot be fixed currently,
# either because the patched version is not yet published to PyPI, 
# or because the vulnerability is a false positive from base image metadata.

# python-dotenv: CVE fixed in 1.2.2, but latest on PyPI is 1.2.1
CVE-2026-28684

# requests: CVE fixed in 2.33.0, but latest on PyPI is 2.32.5
CVE-2026-25645

# pip: Fixed in 25.3/26.0. Upgrading pip via pip leaves dist-info metadata
# which Trivy still flags. Ignoring these base image alerts.
CVE-2025-8869
CVE-2026-1703
